summary: The official office for the Archmage of Winterhold College. First part of a planned tower residence named Drakespire
descriptionHtml:
This is the first part of a planned Archmage tower called Drakespire. It is an office for the Archmage, with a portal from the quarters at Winterhold College. 

Includes:

5 Mannequins
4 Weapon Racks (4 slots each)
2 Chests
1 Strongbox
1 Pet Raven
author: mgbeach
